snippet.title: Barbie Software: Groovy Games GBA - C&M Playthrough
snippet.description:
Hit the town with Barbie and her friends for fun and adventure!

Travel to groovy locations and play the coolest games! Cruise to the beach for a far-out game of checkers, or drop by the toy store to play hangman a whole new way! Only Barbie can give these cool favorites a hip, new style! With nine games to choose from, you'll have hours of on-the-go fun!

Platform: Game Boy Advance

Developer: Digital Illusions
Publisher: VU Games

Release: September 4, 2002
